      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It has been well-maintained and runs reliably, with only minor cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior consistent with regular use. All major systems are functional.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
